# Desh - An Idea

Ernest Renan, delivered a lecture at the Sorbonne University on March 11th, 1882, on the topic - Qu’est-ce qu’une nation? (What is a Nation?). This lecture ponders over some important questions about the idea of a Nation. What becomes and what unbecomes a nation.

